&lt;p&gt;Entera is looking for long-term, career-oriented individuals who want to be part of changing the way people buy and sell real estate.&amp;nbsp; We are heavily invested in your success and offer opportunities to expand your professional growth, such as employer-paid licensing and multi-state and multi-market experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Only&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;accepting applicants from the following states: &lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;AZ, FL, TX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
